                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for preparing methane from hydrogen and carbon and recovering heat source",
                    "一种氢碳制甲烷与热源回收的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for preparing methane from hydrogen and carbon and recovering a heat source, which belongs to the technical field of renewable energy sources and comprises the following steps: (1) recovering heat released by absorbing CO2 by adopting cooling water; (2) recovering low-temperature heat of 100 DEG C and below by adopting cooling water; (3) mixing the hot water subjected to heat recovery in the step (1) and the step (2), introducing hydrogen in a water electrolysis hydrogen production cycle into the hot water, and carrying out water evaporation by utilizing hydrogen purging to obtain water vapor; (4) introducing the mixed gas of water vapor and hydrogen obtained in the step (3) into a hydrocarbon-to-methane reactor, carrying out hydrogen-carbon-to-methane, and recovering heat released from hydrocarbon-to-methane by using water vapor; and (5) sensible heat of reaction gas for hydrogen production through electrolysis and methane production through hydrocarbon is recycled through water evaporation and is used for energy consumption of absorbent regeneration. Different heat recovery modes are adopted for heat sources with different temperatures, the comprehensive energy utilization rate of the system is improved, and energy consumption is reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种氢碳制甲烷与热源回收的方法，属于可再生能源技术领域，包括以下步骤：(1)采用冷却水将CO2吸收放出的热量进行回收；(2)采用冷却水将100℃及以下的低温热量进行回收；(3)将步骤(1)和步骤(2)热回收的热水进行混合，将电解水制氢循环的氢气通入热水中，利用氢气吹扫进行水蒸发，得到水蒸气；(4)将步骤(3)得到的水蒸气和氢气混合气通入碳氢制甲烷反应器，进行氢碳制甲烷，并采用水蒸气对碳氢制甲烷放出热量的回收；(5)利用水蒸发回收电解制氢和碳氢制甲烷反应气的显热，并用于吸收剂再生的能耗。通过对不同温度的热源采用不同的热回收方式，提高系统的综合能量利用率，降低能耗。"
                }
            ]
